{"tid":1944194,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵按機制再加價2.55%","createTime":"2020-03-26T08:40:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T09:03:51.000Z","uid":351543,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"60a3accf2e923a8217bf4631623da0f77cd567ff","tid":1944194,"uid":351543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T08:40:18.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母呀而家咩時期啊仲加價"},{"pid":"f6e1bbac43c319a7a7af58e4c4a80ad230a5779e","tid":1944194,"uid":99700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T08:41:05.000Z","msg":"唔搭驚閪 話之佢加255%"},{"pid":"3a0ff404ae2f46ebb1ee7354bdec5d359d310b7e","tid":1944194,"uid":59451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T08:41:20.000Z","msg":"可加可減<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c1c4b6925f4b262f03e61da1648ffff83d3c4fa","tid":1944194,"uid":33441,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T08:42:08.000Z","msg":"根本就係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">可加可加</span></strong>機制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d8cd7f92d53cda443ac42d1459b04f651a5a45","tid":1944194,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T08:46:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />市民再按機制使用廢老卡"},{"pid":"785b91ed436b4a08785ed00ae007fc7aa1e75439","tid":1944194,"uid":8572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T09:03:51.000Z","msg":"政府統計處今日（26日）公布去年12月運輸業名義工資指數變動為3.4%。按照港鐵票價調整方程式計算，連同早前公布的去年12月通脹指數為2.9%，減去額外的0.6%扣減，得出的結果是2.55%。換言之，新一年度的港鐵票價將可加價2.55%。<br />\n港鐵其後發新聞稿指，因應機制內設「負擔能力上限」封頂機票，故實際票價將維持不變。同時又指，因應新冠肺炎疫情對本港造成影響，故宣布推出一系列超過7億元的車費優惠，包括將現有的「程程3.3%車費扣減」優惠、「港鐵都會票」及「屯門-南昌全日通」的現行售價延至明年1月1日。"}]}